<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>8877</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>12699</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗孚该体检了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12700</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18793</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可是，罗孚不想去看兽医。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18794</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23618</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快点儿，罗孚！” 妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23619</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27495</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾米推，哈利拉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27496</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32415</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，狗狗拒绝进动物医院。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32416</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37828</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我理解你。” 奥利弗对罗孚说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37829</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42182</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也不喜欢去看医生。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42183</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46118</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奥利弗看着妈妈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46119</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52406</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也许，得给罗孚点儿零食了。” 他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52407</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58247</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，罗孚就坐在候诊室里了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58248</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65161</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它走来走去，喘着气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65162</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70411</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我理解你。” 奥利弗对狗说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70412</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75721</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“等着看医生的时候，我也很紧张。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75722</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奥利弗看着妈妈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79236</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83995</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“给罗孚点儿零食吧！” 他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83996</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗孚和它的家人们走进了诊疗室。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90503</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93759</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>里面变得很拥挤。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93760</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98039</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>兽医给罗孚称了体重。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98040</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104946</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>接着，她又看了看它的眼睛、耳朵和嘴巴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104947</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111647</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的医生也是这么做的！” 奥利弗对罗孚说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111648</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116637</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>兽医听了听罗孚的心脏和肺。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116638</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120826</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们的狗很健康！” 她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120827</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124360</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在，该给它打针了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124361</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“打针？我讨厌打针！” 奥利弗大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130919</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135346</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奥利弗一下子冲到诊疗桌下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135347</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140635</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗孚也飞快地冲到了桌子下面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140636</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144844</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>其他人互相看着对方。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144845</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149860</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“给罗孚点儿零食吧！” 哈利说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149861</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156925</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也给奥利弗一些！” 艾米说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
